features: Crafted with Wood and Acrylic Brilliance: Behold, the mesmerizing fusion of wood and acrylic in this mini itx case! It's a DIY delight for geeks and an envy-inducing showstopper for every gathering!
Build Like a Pro: Building this small pc case has no more headaches! Detailed instructions, a full toolkit, and high-quality screws are included in the package, making your build a walk in the park.
Your PC Case, Your Canvas: Wooden cases are easier to color up. The wooden exterior is your canvas – paint it, personalize it, and make it your own.
Cable Chaos? Not Here!: The unique dual chamber pc case, with its wooden chamber, conceals all wires. We also provide cable ties for efficient cable management, helping you achieve a tidy setup.
Storage Superhero: You can even use the micro itx case as a NAS case. Look no further! This pc case houses rocks up to 6 slick 2.5-inch SATA hard drives, giving you storage powers galore.

Efficient airflow pc case: The mini tower pc case with three 92mm case fan slots, channeling a cyclone of airflow. Heat escapes swiftly through smart vents, keeping you in the gaming zone without a hitch.
Embrace Open Air: If you remove the acrylic part then it will be an open air pc case, make you enjoy the freedom of an open frame computer case for optimal airflow. It's also a test bench pc case.

Extra-Long GPU Support: Goodbye size limits! This is not just a mini PC case, it's a gaming PC case with a unique design. An extra-long GPU can gracefully extend through the specially crafted openings.
No More Acrylic Hassles: Installation made simple! We've ditched the pesky acrylic films, making PC building a breeze.

Hardware Compatibility: 17x17mm mini ITX motherboard; GPU thickness: Max 1.65" (42mm); GPU height: Max 4.72" (120mm); GPU length: Preferably within 7.68" (195mm, Oversized cards extend through front openings ); CPU Fan up to 4.96"( 126mm) height; SFX PSU; Up to 6 x 2.5" SATA HDD/SSD; Up to 3 x 92mm or smaller case fans (One 92mm wide, 25mm thick or smaller fan at the back; Two 92mm wide fans, each with a thickness of 15mm or smaller, on the side).
body.description: Elevate your PC-building experience with our Premium Acrylic+Wood ITX PC Case! Crafted with a unique design, our mini itx case features beautiful and transparent acrylic panels combined with the warmth of wood, making it a real showstopper. Get ready for a DIY adventure! Our case comes with detailed installation instructions and a tool kit, ensuring you have everything you need to build your dream machine right out of the box. Enjoy the excitement of building your custom PC and impress itx pc case friends with your craftsmanship. Efficient cable management is essential for a clean and organized build. Our case cleverly conceals cable clutter, ensuring your setup looks sleek and professional. Stay cool under pressure! Our case supports up to three cooling fans of 9.2cm size or smaller, guaranteeing optimal airflow during intense gaming sessions. Abundant ventilation prevents overheating. Keep components cool for smooth gaming. You can even use it as an open frame computer case. Unleash your creativity with our Premium Acrylic+Wood ITX PC Case – a showcase of innovation, style, and performance. Elevate your PC-building journey today! Hardware Compatibility: 17x17mm mini ITX motherboard; GPU thickness: Max 1.65" (42mm); GPU height: Max 4.72" (120mm); GPU length: Preferably within 7.68" (195mm, Oversized cards extend through front openings ); Air coolers up to 4.96"( 126mm) height; SFX PSU only; Up to 6 x 2.5" SATA HDD/SSD; Up to 3 x 92mm or smaller cooling fans ( One 92mm wide, 25mm thick or smaller fan at the back; Two 92mm wide, 15mm thick or smaller fans on the side ). Dimensions: 8.05" W x 8.87" L x 9.92" H ( Height including 0.71" case feet)

reviews.reviewText: I love it and it’s very unique but you are limited on gpu size. I had the 3070 dual fan and it was sticking out which I had no problem but it was the thickness that wouldn’t allow me to fit the other two acrylic sides in. Luckily I had a 3060 single fan to switch and it was perfect. It’s a pc that I can easily move around when o need to.
